It's unstable, but it's got a VERY pastel theme.

SUPPORT US:

If SOMEHOW CIVIT ISN'T WORKING WE WILL ALWAYS HAVE A BACKUP: https://huggingface.co/Duskfallcrew/

MIX LINE:

  • Includes EpicMixV4 - The Anime version

  • https://civitai.com/models/31295/universal-solvent-mix

  • Three of our really horrid manga models we trained LOL.

  • Anything 4.5 at literally 20 percent on the scale XD - This model is included in Nocrypt's notebook, and i don't have a link.

  • White Space

  • Blue Pastel (This was like at 10percent or less just to help get it more stable)

  • Ekmix Pastel

  • Illusion Mix

  • Paint Style Lora

  • And then again at like a seriously low percent we re merged the Epic Mix pastel base
